Iron Man / Robert Downey Jr vælger OnePlus
OnePlus har virkelig tænkt stort, når det handler om at vise muskelkraften i OnePlus 7 Pro. Først kom publicity stuntet med at løfte en kæmpe cementblok med telefonens pop-up-kamera, og nu har de fået selveste Iron Man i skikkelse af Robert Downey Jr. til at erklære til sin støtte til selskabet og deres nye telefon.Artiklen […].

title: Leave the War with Me
body:
by Blaithin

Steve had been shot before. But most bullets didn’t drag him back and forth through time.

As he struggles with a worsening injury and his own complicated feelings following the SHRA, Steve realises that it isn’t his timeline he is jumping through but Tony’s. And the time jumps seem to be leading somewhere, to something worse than he could ever have imagined.

title: You're not Dead?
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2HQj3c8

by bethy_277

This was done for an anon prompt on Agib’s Tumblr. I saw it, and asked for permission to write it.

The request was Peter thinks that Tony is dead, and Tony keeps it that way to keep Peter safe, only Pepper, Rhodey and Happy know he’s alive. It’s not until Peter starts to go towards suicide that Tony steps in and tells Peter he did it to protect him.

I took it a little further.
